---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title="Programs | FitMom702" description="Fitness programs by Audrey at FitMom702" />
  </head>

  <body>

    <Header />

    <main>

      <h1>FitMom702 Programs</h1>

      <p>
      Welcome to the FitMom702 training programs created by Audrey,
      certified personal trainer and kettlebell coach helping women
      build strength, confidence, and consistency.
      </p>

      <h2>KettleBaddie Summer Program</h2>

      <p>
      A 6-week kettlebell program designed to help you build glutes,
      tone your body, and increase overall strength. Perfect for busy
      moms who want real results without spending hours in the gym.
      </p>

      <h2>Custom Coaching</h2>

      <p>
      Personalized fitness coaching designed around your goals,
      schedule, and experience level. Get structured workouts,
      accountability, and support.
      </p>

      <h2>Monthly Challenges</h2>

      <p>
      Join the FitMom702 community challenges to stay motivated,
      track progress, and stay consistent every month.
      </p>

    </main>

    <Footer />

  </body>
</html>
